description.percentChange1m: 1-Month Percent Change: The percent difference between the current price and the settlement price from 1 month ago.
description.percentChange1y: 52-Week Percent Change: The difference between the current price and the settlement price from 1 year ago expressed as a percentage.

description.hasOptions: The symbol either has options available, or does not.
description.symbolType: A Call option gives you the right to buy a stock and a Put option gives you the right to sell a stock.
